msgid "Member of Kanemura Enterprises, a third tier group of the Tojo Clan. With an affable personality that lacks the affectations of a typical yakuza, he has the complete trust of his superior, Arai Pursues Ihara after he shoots Arai at Club Elnard. Returns to the family office after losing Ihara's trail and finds Kanemura dead. Currently trying to save Arai by finding him before the police or the Tojo Clan. Kido is attacked and abducted by Midorikawa from the Hatsushiba Family, who is in league with the Shibata. After losing contact with Arai, he takes an interest in Akiyama due to his connection with Arai."
