msgid "Man who carried out the Ueno Seiwa Attack of 1985. In actuality, he hadn't killed a single soul, as the incident had been orchestrated by Katsuragi and Sugiuchi. Returns to Kamurocho after breaking out of Okinawa Penitentiary No. 2, and reunites with Majima. Learns why Majima never showed on the day of the Ueno Seiwa Attack. Abducted by Katsuragi after an attack on Purgatory."
