msgid "Former fourth chairman of the Tojo Clan and legendary yakuza known as the Dragon of Dojima for the dragon tattoo on his back. Now runs Morning Glory Orphanage in Okinawa. Returns to Kamurocho with Yasuko, who is looking for Saejima, but both she and Saejima are abducted by Katsuragi. Attempts to trade the secret file for Yasuko's safety, but she perishes while protecting Saejima and the file is stolen by Arai. Clashes with Daigo, who chose to cause mayhem to protect the clan, on the roof of Millennium Tower. Feels responsible for Daigo's burden."
