msgctxt "95839	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A detective who loves gambling so much that he often listens to horse races or plays mahjong while on duty. Known as the Parasite of Kamurocho, he collects hush money from illegal businesses. Questioned by Sugiuchi for leaving fingerprints on Ihara's body at the crime scene on March 1st. Reprimanded by his boss, Hisai, when a complaint comes in about him taking money from civilians through mahjong. Was tracking down the snitch who ratted him out. Received a message from Zhao and is currently heading towards the Chinese restaurant, Homeland."
