msgctxt "97997	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Known as the Parasite of Kamurocho, he collects hush money from illegal businesses, but actually uses the money to support local orphans. His father was killed 25 years ago while investigating the Ueno Seiwa Attack. Had been searching for Yasuko Saejima, with whom his father was to meet before his death. Learns from Yasuko that his father discovered another person was responsible for the incident, and was killed as a result. Now trying to get the 100 million yen Yasuko borrowed from Akiyama in order to negotiate with Katsuragi, who knows the truth."
