msgid "Known as the Parasite of Kamurocho, he collects hush money from illegal businesses, but actually uses the money to support local orphans. Continues to search for the truth about his father's death during the investigation of the Ueno Seiwa Attack 25 years ago. Learns from Katsuragi that his father discovered that another person was responsible and was killed to avoid exposure of police involvement. Discovers Katsuragi was the one responsible, but fails to find his father's killer. Came to Archive Room 13 with Hisai for evidence of police corruption."
